data.description: Welcome Home!!! This is a beautiful remodeled 3-bedroom 2-bath home. This home features updated laminate flooring, carpet, casement windows throughout the home, and cedar walls installed with a modern flare, quartz countertops, and new self-closing cabinets with updated stainless-steel appliances. Walk-in laundry room with cedar walls, includes new washer & and dryer. The master bedroom & and living room have vaulted ceilings. The master bedroom has a new carpet and a walk-in closet. This home sits on 1 acre of land, with a newly built modern back deck for family gatherings. The patio future, grill, a fire pit is included with the sale of the home. The home also includes a recently built outside storage building (16X12) and a fenced backyard. No HOA’s This home is a Must SEE!!!!
